So far we have looked into KBs for cardinality detection, but the KBs are usually sparse. Even if we have identified that numberOfDoctoralStudents is a counting predicate, we cannot predict its value for an entity that has the enumerating predicate doctoralStudent but no counting predicate numberOfDoctoralStudents.